Cell.Text: Now we have the witches' heads, we must go to Ysgramor's Tomb, and burn them in the Harbinger Flame.
We did... Kodlak has paid for his mistake, but now his soul may rest from its torment... | I'm thinking.. I fear his price was too high...
Yes, I agree with you. And now the war is over. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic02: Now the Companions are cleaned from Hircine curse. I think it was worth.

Cell.Text: He allowed the Companions to kill Krev. He deserved it!
Yes, Krev perished as well... | But I hope Kodlak and Krev are right now on Sovngarde putting all the anger and hate aside, and sharing a sweet mead mug. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic03: He allowed the Companions to kill Krev. He deserved it!

Cell.Text: I think you are right. But now we cannot go back in time...
Yes. But at least the companions are free from this ancient curse. And we are not enemies anymore. I hope our legates may rejoin again some day. | I have one more thing to ask.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic04: I think you are right. But now we cannot go back in time...

Cell.Text: I think you should be the leader of the Silver Hands. | I really think I'm better with my research than with leadership. | If it wasn't for you, we wouldn't have made it. | Do you accept?
[S] Good. Hillara and Sennar are responsible for managing the contracts. | Talk to them to organize the wolf hunts. | Please, hold this axe and kill some beasts for me.
[S] I also would like to ask for you to come back to Driftshade in a few days. I'm finishing another research.
I think I'm not ready for this yet...
[S] I understand. If you change your mind, come talk to me on Driftshade. | Hillara and Sennar are responsible for managing the contracts on Gallows Rock.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_ASK_Topic08: I think I'm not ready for this yet...

Cell.Text: I decide to accept the Silver Hands' leadership.

[S] Good. I know you were going to accept. | Talk to Hillara and Senaar to organize the wolf hunts and contracts. Also, talk to him about how to improve the leader's quarters. | Please, hold this axe and kill some beasts.

Node.Caption: DSilHand_M90_DAL_Topic01: I decide to accept the Silver Hands' leadership.
